Gonzalez, Griswold
</taxonomicName>
, and Engel, 
<taxonomicNameLabel pageId="51" rank="species">new species</taxonomicNameLabel>
(paratype, SEMC 1178928). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[498,523,1623,1647]" pageId="51">A.</emphasis>
Sixth tergum, dorsal view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[823,880,1623,1647]" pageId="51">B, D.</emphasis>
Seventh tergum in dorsal and ventral views. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[267,291,1652,1676]" pageId="51">C.</emphasis>
Fifth sternum. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[465,487,1653,1677]" pageId="51">E.</emphasis>
Sixth sternum. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[664,682,1653,1677]" pageId="51">F.</emphasis>
Eighth sternum. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[875,925,1652,1676]" pageId="51">G–I.</emphasis>
